    /**
     World-space 3D axis-aligned bounding box (AABB).

     Represented by a six-element Float32Array containing the min/max extents of the
     axis-aligned volume, ie. ````[xmin, ymin,zmin,xmax,ymax, zmax]````.

     @property aabb
     @final
